vers, dining table covers, and yoga mats; dinnerware, serve ware, tabletops, cutlery, drinkware, tea and coffee products, and table linens; and cook and bakeware, food preps and tools, storage solutions, and table and kitchen linens. Further, it provides towel and laundry products; bath and cleaning accessories; kitchen and home appliances; idols and figurines, candles, holders, vases and flowers, and garden products; wall and d\u00e9cor accents; and lamps. Additionally, the company is involved in the distribution of international beauty brands. It offers its products through HomeStop and Shoppers Stop stores, as well as through mobile applications and website. Shoppers Stop Limited was founded in 1991 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}